  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    ‘Build the Future’ announced as theme for National Apprenticeship Week 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The theme for the 14th annual National Apprenticeship Week has been announced today – Tuesday 1 December.</p>

  </div>
</div>

